data.description: GORGEOUS 3Bed + 2Bath + 2Car in Meadowlake Farms Gated Community! This Home Flows Wonderfully into each Main Living Space that Feels Completely Open ~ Kitchen Boasts LARGE Island, Stainless Steel Appliances, & Pantry ~ Crown Molding throughout ~ All New Paint ~ BEAUTIFUL Wood Floors in Living Room, Primary Ensuite, & both Guest Bedrooms ~ SPACIOUS Living Room with LOVELY Fireplace ~ Primary Ensuite has Double Vanities, Walk-in Closet with Built-ins ~ GRAND Laundry Room with LOTS of Storage + Connects to the Primary Ensuite ~ Built-in Linen Closet by Guest Bathroom ~ Guest Bathroom Connects to 2nd Guest Bedroom ~ BIG Back Patio, Perfect for Entertaining ~ Wrought Iron Fence with Professional Landscaping around Property ~ Attic Auto Lift ~ Epoxy Garage Floor ~Welcome Home!
